{"word":"G4841 - συμπάσχω - sympáschō - soom-pas'-kho - Suffer with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπάσχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sympáschō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom-pas'-kho</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Suffer with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடப் பாடுபடு"},{"paragraph":"to suffer or feel pain together"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G3958 - πάσχω - páschō - pas'-kho/3958\">G3958</a> (including its alternate); to <i>experience pain jointly</i> or of the <i>same kind</i> (specifically <i>persecution</i>; to &ldquo;sympathize&rdquo;): - suffer with.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2552/2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553/2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3356/3356\">G3356</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663/3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3804/3804\">G3804</a>, <a href=\"#/G3805/3805\">G3805</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806/3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958/3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236/4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310/4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4776/4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777/4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789/4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800/4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806/4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821/4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832/4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833/4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4834/4834\">G4834</a>, <a href=\"#/G4835/4835\">G4835</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841/4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854/4854\">G4854</a>,